    independently.</p>

  <p>I had the remarkable experience of
    <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/simonblink24/sets/72157625051285708/">
      visiting Chernobyl in September 2010</a> and returning radiation free!</p>

  <p>In 2012 I drove across California in a Mustang, visiting places such as Yosemite,
  Death Valley and Silicon Valley. The latter included visits to the Github and Mozilla offices, because geek.</p>
</div>
